{"tid":1275343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"失望","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T20:43:45.000Z","uid":199983,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92d5bcffb7ddf715a60225e99eb99fe4f5d037e3","tid":1275343,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:15:40.000Z","msg":"今日發生咗小小事，係第二個post到發表咗一下我嘅感受。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想知如果我之前參與遊行唔小心受傷，我老豆會唔會都話抵死，好似話片中被人詆毀個女仔咁話我？<br />\n<br />\n我老豆由六月到今日之前都無對依加社會發生緊嘅事表態過，我都無問過，其實我覺得咁都幾好，點知到到今日，兩個字『抵死』，真係好撚委屈。<br />\n其他親戚share假料我嬲，對住屋企人係失望。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點形容我依加嘅心情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPoc7KA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPoc7KA.png&h=14f74e2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5208e51561e1b22f4c77a6100fe05b90021ebd0b","tid":1275343,"uid":259776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:19:02.000Z","msg":"你仲有一班同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a47e0202c7a676b60d0ec1c3d721077c5300879","tid":1275343,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5208e51561e1b22f4c77a6100fe05b90021ebd0b","tid":1275343,"uid":259776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:19:02.000Z","msg":"你仲有一班同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"多謝你，老實講，我見到咁多人咁努力，係我最大嘅動力"},{"pid":"8c816f17a893bc76c69d4a1b63f47c0d42d2c154","tid":1275343,"uid":259776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a47e0202c7a676b60d0ec1c3d721077c5300879","tid":1275343,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5208e51561e1b22f4c77a6100fe05b90021ebd0b","tid":1275343,"uid":259776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:19:02.000Z","msg":"你仲有一班同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"多謝你，老實講，我見到咁多人咁努力，係我最大嘅動力